## 1. Structure of the Guitar

**String Mapping:**

1.  **Navier–Stokes:** Fluid dynamics (Flow, chaos, energy dissipation)
2.  **Yang–Mills Mass Gap:** Field theory (Confinement, vacuum structure)
3.  **Riemann Hypothesis:** Number theory (Zero distribution, frequency spectrum)
4.  **P vs NP:** Complexity theory (Verification vs generation)
5.  **Hodge Conjecture:** Algebraic geometry (Correspondence between topology & algebra)
6.  **Birch–Swinnerton-Dyer:** Arithmetic geometry (Rank of elliptic curves)
7.  **Connes Noncommutative Field (Harmonic):** Hidden layer (Operator algebras, symmetry breaking)

**All seven together form a resonant mathematical lattice.**

